{"search_data": "Himachal PradeshMukhyamantri Him Seva Helpline Number in Himachal Pradesh Mukhyamantri Him Seva Helpline Number to launch in Himachal Pradesh, HP CM Him Seva toll free no. to address people's problems, talk to CM on phone, suggestions invited at cmoffice-hp@gov.in \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902HP Mukhyamantri Him Seva Helpline NumberAt the call center setup by the Himachal Pradesh government, an official attending the call placed at Mukhyamantri Him Seva Helpline number will note down the problem. He will then feed it inside the computer and the problem would then be forwarded to the concerned official. That official will have to take time bound action on that problem and address that problem.As soon as the proper action is taken on the problem, then the complainant would be given information regarding this. Chief Minister Jairam Thakur will review the functioning of CM Him Seva Helpline No. every month. CMO Himachal Pradesh has prepared a completed draft action plan for implementation of this toll free number.In the newly setup call center, dozens of officials will sit together to address problems of people. Moreover, the software in which the call attendant has to feed the problem is already prepared and is in final stage of testing.\u0926\u0947\u0935\u092d\u0942\u092e\u093f \u0939\u093f\u092e\u093e\u091a\u0932 \u0915\u0940 \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0917\u0924\u093f \u090f\u0935\u0902 \u092c\u0947\u0939\u0924\u0930 \u0938\u0941\u0936\u093e\u0938\u0928 \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f \u092a\u094d\u0930\u0926\u0947\u0936 \u0938\u0930\u0915\u093e\u0930 \u0915\u094b \u0908-\u092e\u0947\u0932 \u0915\u0947 \u092e\u093e\u0927\u094d\u092f\u092e \u0938\u0947 cmoffice-hp@gov.in \u092a\u0930 \u0905\u092a\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u0940\u092e\u0924\u0940 \u0938\u0941\u091d\u093e\u0935 \u0905\u0935\u0936\u094d\u092f \u092d\u0947\u091c\u0947\u0902\u0964#\u0936\u093f\u0916\u0930\u0915\u0940\u0913\u0930\u0939\u093f\u092e\u093e